In re Resignation of Greenwald.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Greenwald (1992), 64 Ohio St.3d 1206.]

(No. 92-955 Submitted June 2, 1992 Decided June 3, 1992.)

The resignation of Michael I. Greenwald as an attorney, Registration No. 0025083, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
